  "An object at rest has a net force of zero. If F1 = (5, 8) N and F2 = (-2, -3) N, what must F3 be for equilibrium?": "",
  "(-7, -11) N": "",
  "(3, 5) N": "",
  "(7, 11) N": "",
  "(-3, -5) N": "",
  "For equilibrium, F1 + F2 + F3 = (0, 0). So F3 = -(F1 + F2) = -((5-2, 8-3)) = -(3, 5) = (-3, -5) N.": "",
